00:13:02.726 --> 00:13:04.518
<i>That man got back at me.</i>

215
00:13:06.018 --> 00:13:08.935
<i>He broke into my house</i>
<i>and took all my money.</i>


216
00:13:11.476 --> 00:13:14.518
<i>I needed to run away
as fast as I could.</i>

217
00:13:20.685 --> 00:13:25.060
For fuck's sake! Did I kill you?

218
00:13:25.143 --> 00:13:27.476
Sorry, I can't help you right now.

219
00:13:29.518 --> 00:13:31.935
Lohane? Did you have to show up now?

220
00:13:32.018 --> 00:13:35.185
<i>You think he had a bad day? 
