228
00:14:03.893 --> 00:14:06.768
-We have a delicious juice for free.
-Awesome!


229
00:14:06.851 --> 00:14:10.643
Artificial cashew fruit flavor
never found in nature.


230
00:14:11.643 --> 00:14:13.976
