595
00:33:02.685 --> 00:33:05.976
Not having money, that's how I did it.

596
00:33:06.060 --> 00:33:07.310
Let's keep an eye out.

597
00:33:07.393 --> 00:33:09.851
They'll come after us,
and I've only just started.


598
00:33:09.935 --> 00:33:12.268
BOAT RIDES

599
00:33:17.185 --> 00:33:19.018
Wasn't this supposed to be fast?

600
00:33:19.560 --> 00:33:22.893
We've been here for hours.
I'm on my fifth slushy.


601
00:33:22.976 --> 00:33:26.435
We're studying the area.
Do you see that boat ride agency?


602
00:33:26.518 --> 00:33:28.101
They only take cash or checks.

603
00:33:28.185 --> 00:33:31.768
We must wait
for someone to pay with a check,


604
00:33:31.851 --> 00:33:33.976
take a picture of the signature,

605
00:33:34.060 --> 00:33:36.601
then forge a new check
and exchange it with the original.


606
00:33:36.685 --> 00:33:39.393
