665
00:36:27.101 --> 00:36:31.101
She gave you the wrong one
and asked me to get it back


666
00:36:31.185 --> 00:36:32.768
and give you this one.

667
00:36:32.851 --> 00:36:33.726
-Okay?
-Right.


668
00:36:33.810 --> 00:36:36.351
It's all the same,
but the bank is different.


669
00:36:36.851 --> 00:36:39.893
-All right, then.
-Could you hurry up?


670
00:36:39.976 --> 00:36:42.726
She's waiting outside,
and she's in a terrible mood.


671
00:36:43.310 --> 00:36:44.601
-You know?
-Yes.


672
00:36:45.435 --> 00:36:48.810
-Impatient. She's…
-I'll just check it.


673
00:36:48.893 --> 00:36:51.185
-It's all the same but the bank.
-Okay.


674
00:36:51.268 --> 00:36:52.643
-All right.
-Awesome.


675
00:36:52.726 --> 00:36:54.851
-Thank you.
-You're welcome.


676
00:36:55.476 --> 00:36:56.935
<i>Eleven thousand reais.</i>

677
00:36:58.976 --> 00:37:01.685
