725
00:39:22.310 --> 00:39:23.935
We become criminals.

726
00:39:24.018 --> 00:39:26.185
We take out our phones, keys, everything.

727
00:39:26.268 --> 00:39:27.810
They ask for our pacemakers.

728
00:39:27.893 --> 00:39:30.893
Someone might have
a heart attack right here.


729
00:39:30.976 --> 00:39:34.560
And it's all the bank's fault!

730
00:39:34.643 --> 00:39:35.976
That's right!

731
00:39:36.060 --> 00:39:38.393
We want respect!

732
00:39:39.893 --> 00:39:43.393
Respect! We want respect!

733
00:39:44.685 --> 00:39:47.851
Listen, I'm not holding up the line
because I want to.


734
00:39:47.935 --> 00:39:49.601
