1283
01:10:22.060 --> 01:10:23.060
Get me some water.

1284
01:10:25.935 --> 01:10:27.976
Taste is good, but money is money.

1285
01:10:28.060 --> 01:10:30.893
You might not like a Picasso
in your living room,


1286
01:10:30.976 --> 01:10:33.810
but you'll love a Picasso
in your bank account.


1287
01:10:34.976 --> 01:10:37.351
