Done.

1290
01:10:41.185 --> 01:10:42.435
But be discreet.

1291
01:10:42.935 --> 01:10:45.310
Pretend you received some nudes.

1292
01:10:46.060 --> 01:10:47.310
Which is also true

1293
01:10:47.393 --> 01:10:50.351
because the artist strips for the art.

1294
01:10:51.518 --> 01:10:55.685
I told you. It's amazing.

1295
01:10:55.768 --> 01:10:57.518
-Thirty thousand?
-A hundred.


1296
01:10:57.601 --> 01:11:00.643
No, I'm sorry. 
That's one installment.

1297
01:11:00.726 --> 01:11:03.685
We sell it for 100,
but I'll sell it to you for 90.


1298
01:11:04.226 --> 01:11:06.768
-Or no deal. Stand your ground.
-Or no deal.


1299
01:11:06.851 --> 01:11:08.143
Stand your ground.

1300
01:11:11.518 --> 01:11:12.351
So?

1301
01:11:16.060 --> 01:11:16.893
No deal.

1302
01:11:17.643 --> 01:11:18.768
Motherfucker.

1303
01:11:20.768 --> 01:11:24.351
I got rejected for something
I didn't even want, Clóvis.


1304
01:11:24.435 --> 01:11:26.935
It's all your fault. What now?

1305
01:11:32.060 --> 01:11:34.060
"Fifty grand and it's a deal."

1306
01:11:37.476 --> 01:11:38.435
Deal.

1307
01:11:53.143 --> 01:11:54.601
Can you hear me, Clóvis?

1308
01:11:54.685 --> 01:11:55.685
<i>Loud and clear.</i>

1309
01:11:55.768 --> 01:11:59.018
<i>Act naturally,</i>
<i>like you're an honest person.</i>


1310
01:11:59.101 --> 01:12:01.560
I don't know how. 
I was born dishonest.

1311
01:12:01.643 --> 01:12:04.685
Don't answer me!
They'll think you're crazy.


1312
01:12:05.268 --> 01:12:07.185
They already do.

1313
01:12:07.268 --> 01:12:10.351
I'm a medium. I'm here for your family.

1314
01:12:10.435 --> 01:12:14.518
The deceased just checked into Heaven.
Everything is fine.


1315
01:12:14.601 --> 01:12:16.226
Your energy is murky.

1316
01:12:16.310 --> 01:12:17.726
I'll pray for you.

1317
01:12:18.268 --> 01:12:19.185
God damn it!

1318
01:12:20.143 --> 01:12:21.643
Are you dead or alive?

1319
01:12:21.726 --> 01:12:23.560
The man coming, is he alive?

1320
01:12:23.643 --> 01:12:24.935
That's Fortunato.

1321
01:12:26.435 --> 01:12:28.268
-Jesus!
-Fortunato. Nice to meet you.


1322
01:12:28.351 --> 01:12:31.268
Don't do that,
we can't tell if you're alive.


1323
01:12:31.351 --> 01:12:32.393
You're like a ghost.

1324
01:12:32.476 --> 01:12:36.393
São Paulo was built
on top of an indigenous cemetery.


1325
01:12:36.476 --> 01:12:39.851
São Paulo is a double-decker cemetery.

1326
01:12:39.935 --> 01:12:41.976
The energy here is so murky.

1327
01:12:42.060 --> 01:12:44.643
I've got goosebumps. 
What the hell?

1328
01:12:44.726 --> 01:12:46.185
I'm here for the painting.

1329
01:12:46.268 --> 01:12:49.351
About that, I'm not the counterfeiter.

1330
01:12:49.435 --> 01:12:53.643
I'm a medium,
and I use spirituality to paint.


1331
01:12:53.726 --> 01:12:56.601
I don't use my hands.
It's a unique technique.


1332
