1338
01:13:11.226 --> 01:13:13.851
Yes!

1339
01:13:13.935 --> 01:13:16.643
Too many people talking at the same time.

1340
01:13:16.726 --> 01:13:17.601
I apologize.

1341
01:13:17.685 --> 01:13:20.226
I have a great connection.
They're so close.


1342
01:13:20.310 --> 01:13:25.393
There are great artists buried here, okay?
They're talking to me.


1343
01:13:25.476 --> 01:13:29.768
They're very happy with our deal.
It's the deal of a lifetime, or death.


1344
01:13:31.185 --> 01:13:32.018
