1345
01:13:34.101 --> 01:13:36.143
Say there's something in your eye.

1346
01:13:36.226 --> 01:13:39.560
-What's going on here?
-Something got in my eyes.


1347
01:13:39.643 --> 01:13:42.310
My eyes! There's something in them.

1348
01:13:42.393 --> 01:13:46.560
-Why is that homeless man looking at us?
-What? Homeless man?


1349
01:13:46.643 --> 01:13:48.476
That one over there?

1350
01:13:48.560 --> 01:13:50.726
I didn't see him. 
He blended in.

1351
01:13:50.810 --> 01:13:53.060
