That's absurd!
Nobody knows a homeless man.


1360
01:14:12.935 --> 01:14:16.393
Who calls them up
and invites them to go have a drink?


1361
01:14:16.476 --> 01:14:19.601
No such thing.
Let's cut to the chase. Your Portinari.


1362
01:14:31.726 --> 01:14:33.018
<i>I told you it would work.</i>

1363
01:14:33.101 --> 01:14:35.768
We're a team. We're a duo!

