Which duo are we?

1368
01:14:49.310 --> 01:14:51.560
Sandy & Junior, obviously.
They're siblings, too.


1369
01:14:51.643 --> 01:14:52.810
I'm Sandy, then!

1370
01:14:54.476 --> 01:14:55.351
I said it first.

1371
01:14:55.435 --> 01:14:58.935
Of course not!
I'm Sandy, I'm a girl. You're Junior.


1372
01:14:59.018 --> 01:15:00.518
I don't wanna be Junior.

1373
01:15:00.601 --> 01:15:03.101
I don't have to. 
I don't relate with him.

