<i>Come to me</i>

1395
01:16:21.935 --> 01:16:25.018
<i>Let's be happy</i>

1396
01:17:06.393 --> 01:17:07.393
Clóvis?

1397
01:17:43.185 --> 01:17:44.351
Good afternoon.

1398
01:17:44.935 --> 01:17:50.143
Welcome to this beautiful event.
You make it beautiful.


1399
01:17:51.268 --> 01:17:54.851
I see we have distinguished people here
this afternoon,


1400
01:17:54.935 --> 01:17:58.393
but the star of the event

1401
01:17:58.476 --> 01:18:02.310
is a very rare piece painted by Portinari.

1402
01:18:02.393 --> 01:18:05.268
Let's take a look at it. Please.

1403
01:18:11.768 --> 01:18:15.268
What a beautiful painting.
I've got goosebumps.


1404
01:18:15.351 --> 01:18:18.810
It's been a while
since I've seen a Portinari so up close.


1405
01:18:20.393 --> 01:18:23.268
The owner of this rare piece of art

1406
01:18:23.351 --> 01:18:26.476
is an eminent personality in Brazil,

1407
01:18:27.226 --> 01:18:31.351
Senator Afonso Narcos,
who is here with us today.


1408
01:18:31.435 --> 01:18:33.060
Please, Senator, stand up.

1409
01:18:33.643 --> 01:18:35.518
Nice suit, Senator.

1410
01:18:36.018 --> 01:18:38.476
Thank you. You may sit down.

1411
01:18:38.560 --> 01:18:43.101
The initial bid for our masterpiece,

1412
