is 800,000 reais.

1414
01:18:47.351 --> 01:18:48.685
Anyone?

1415
01:18:50.060 --> 01:18:52.226
A million! Wonderful!

1416
01:18:52.310 --> 01:18:53.810
A million! Who bids more?

1417
01:18:54.726 --> 01:18:58.060
We have an enthusiast
over there, 1,2 million.


1418
01:18:58.143 --> 01:18:59.351
Who bids more?

1419
01:18:59.435 --> 01:19:01.643
1,4 million.

1420
01:19:01.726 --> 01:19:04.226
Get ready, Clóvis. It's time.

