What are you hiding?

1431
01:19:30.810 --> 01:19:34.018
I'm hiding you from the cops. Go away.

1432
01:19:34.685 --> 01:19:35.601
Excuse me.

1433
01:19:36.185 --> 01:19:39.768
Who bids more? 2,3 million over there.

1434
01:19:39.851 --> 01:19:41.018
