1437
01:19:47.518 --> 01:19:49.310
It's a very close race.

1438
01:19:49.393 --> 01:19:50.560
Who bids more?

1439
01:19:50.643 --> 01:19:52.560
Three million over here!

1440
01:19:53.060 --> 01:19:56.060
The guy who bought it from me
is buying it again?


1441
01:19:56.143 --> 01:19:57.393
What are you up to?

1442
01:19:57.476 --> 01:20:02.185
Sold to the gentleman here.
Congratulations.


1443
01:20:03.060 --> 01:20:04.726
Let's hear it for him.

1444
01:20:04.810 --> 01:20:07.101
I can't explain now. Go away!

1445
01:20:07.185 --> 01:20:09.518
Not until you explain everything.

1446
01:20:09.601 --> 01:20:11.435
You're getting in my way. Go!

1447
01:20:12.018 --> 01:20:13.935
Stop!

1448
01:20:14.018 --> 01:20:15.435
Just for a minute.

1449
01:20:15.518 --> 01:20:17.226
I have something for you.

1450
01:20:17.310 --> 01:20:20.393
Why is a waiter interrupting the auction?

1451
01:20:20.476 --> 01:20:23.310
And some people say
people don't appreciate art.


1452
01:20:23.393 --> 01:20:27.976
Do you plan on bidding?
Did you sign up for the event?


1453
01:20:28.060 --> 01:20:29.560
I'm not here for that.

1454
01:20:29.643 --> 01:20:31.435
I'm here to make an offer.

1455
01:20:31.518 --> 01:20:36.018
If this painting is worth three million,
then tell me something.


1456
01:20:37.768 --> 01:20:39.601
