cheese, lettuce and tomato.


1530
01:24:58.268 --> 01:25:02.393
The Jailbird comes with a chicken patty
and our special sauce.


1531
01:25:02.476 --> 01:25:04.768
The Vegan Fraud tastes like meat,

1532
01:25:04.851 --> 01:25:07.143
but it's eggplant with barbecue sauce.

1533
01:25:07.226 --> 01:25:09.893
And the Crooks' 
Salad is made with tofu.

1534
01:25:09.976 --> 01:25:11.726
-I don't like it.
-I do.


1535
01:25:11.810 --> 01:25:12.976
-Really?
-Sure.


1536
01:25:13.060 --> 01:25:14.351
-Make that two.
-Two?


1537
01:25:14.435 --> 01:25:16.851
Two Crooks' Salads, Lohane!

1538
01:25:16.935 --> 01:25:18.351
Coming right up!

1539
01:25:23.685 --> 01:25:26.226
Now this is a good napkin! It's great!

1540
01:25:26.310 --> 01:25:30.018
I'm proud to serve
good products to my clients.


1541
01:25:30.101 --> 01:25:32.226
Here we have barbecue and mayo.

1542
01:25:32.310 --> 01:25:34.185
Real mayo. It's to die for.

1543
01:25:34.268 --> 01:25:35.435
-Enjoy!
-Thank you.


1544
01:25:35.518 --> 01:25:38.101
Crooks' Salad never made anybody sick.

1545
01:25:38.185 --> 01:25:40.226
Some things are way worse.

1546
01:25:40.310 --> 01:25:42.310
Don't be lazy, Clóvis!

1547
01:25:42.393 --> 01:25:43.893
Get back to work, honey!

1548
01:25:44.601 --> 01:25:47.143
-We gotta pay the bills.
-But I am working!


1549
01:25:47.226 --> 01:25:49.518
Can't you see that? I am working.

1550
01:25:49.601 --> 01:25:53.518
Would you like anything else?
See, I'm working.


1551
01:25:54.893 --> 01:25:56.726
Go make your sandwiches.

1552
01:26:05.810 --> 01:26:08.101
Write down that she had
a Brazilwood phase.


1553
01:26:15.601 --> 01:26:17.060
Unbelievable.

1554
01:26:17.143 --> 01:26:21.060
Impressionists paint
their impression of reality, of beauty.


1555
01:26:23.976 --> 01:26:25.685
-It's boring.
-It's boring.


1556
01:26:25.768 --> 01:26:26.976
Did you come out?

1557
01:26:27.768 --> 01:26:28.935
Are you out yet?

1558
01:26:36.560 --> 01:26:40.768
Cheese-Lohane, Chicken-Lohane,
Lohane-Salad and Ho--


1559
