Try again.

1562
01:26:47.143 --> 01:26:49.851
Yes, I don't have a permit,
I can't sell food,


1563
01:26:49.935 --> 01:26:52.726
but you can't, you can't…

1564
01:26:54.893 --> 01:26:56.726
-Wait!
-Let's go back now!


1565
01:26:56.810 --> 01:26:58.810
-This party is great!
-It sucks!


1566
01:26:58.893 --> 01:27:00.226
Wait, dude!

1567
01:27:00.310 --> 01:27:02.518
Let me go. Why are we leaving?

1568
01:27:02.601 --> 01:27:03.685
Let's go back!

1569
01:27:03.768 --> 01:27:05.518
-Wait, stay here with me.
-Let go.


1570
01:27:05.601 --> 01:27:09.601
-Let go of my arm!
-I won't!


1571
01:27:10.726 --> 01:27:11.810
Let's go to sleep.

1572
01:27:26.643 --> 01:27:27.726
