back to the Air Force?

1575
01:27:35.310 --> 01:27:36.685
What should we do?

1576
01:27:39.226 --> 01:27:42.976
-You serve fake mayonnaise…
-Be careful!


1577
01:27:44.685 --> 01:27:45.601
It's loose.

1578
01:27:45.685 --> 01:27:47.685
For God's sake, don't do that.

1579
01:27:53.226 --> 01:27:54.643
I wanted to be a doctor.

1580
01:27:56.810 --> 01:27:57.893
The problem is

1581
01:27:58.560 --> 01:28:01.601
